title.narrative: IN Second Karnataka Rural Water Supply and Sanitation Project

description.narrative: The project will assist Government of Karnataka (GOK) in: (i) increasing rural communities' access to improved and sustainable drinking water and sanitation services; and (ii) institutionalizing decentralization of Rural Water Supply and Sanitation (RWSS) service delivery to Gram Panchayats (village governments) and user groups.
